effect.full:
User's type changes according to the terrain.

Terrain        | New type
-------------- | --------------
Building       | []{type:normal}
Cave           | []{type:rock}
Desert         | []{type:ground}
Grass          | []{type:grass}
Mountain       | []{type:rock}
Ocean          | []{type:water}
Pond           | []{type:water}
Road           | []{type:ground}
Snow           | []{type:ice}
Tall grass     | []{type:grass}

